-wheels-768x616.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21131728/interview-with-paul-farrell-and-prototype-carbon-bike-wheels-696x558.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21131728/interview-with-paul-farrell-and-prototype-carbon-bike-wheels-1068x857.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21131728/interview-with-paul-farrell-and-prototype-carbon-bike-wheels-524x420.jpg 524w\"></a></p><h3>Want more?</h3><p>If you like this, and you want more great interviews with the people behind the products and brands we all ride, hit subscribe on your favorite podcast player.&nbsp;Find the Bikerumor Podcast on <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/bikerumor-podcast/id1455519558\">Apple Podcasts</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/bikerumor-podcast\">Stitcher</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.podbean.com/\">Podbean</a>, and through <a href=\"https://feed.podbean.com/bikerumor/feed.xml\">RSS</a>, or wherever you listen to podcasts!</p><p>And if you could, give us a quick rating and review, that really helps us grow the audience and keep getting amazing guests for you!</p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>Check <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/podcast/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">all of our podcast interviews</a> for more great stories, and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/podcast-guest-submission/https://bikerumor.com/podcast-guest-submission/https://bikerumor.com/podcast-guest-submission/https://bikerumor.com/podcast-guest-submission/https://bikerumor.com/podcast-guest-submission/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">use this form</a> to let us know who you’d like us to interview next!</p></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8